**60** On the ninth day, the leader of the sons of Benjamin: Abidan the son of Gideoni.

**61** His offering was one silver dish, its weight one hundred and thirty shekels; one silver basin of seventy shekels, according to the shekel of the sanctuary, both of them full of fine flour mixed with oil for a grain offering;

**62** one golden dish of ten shekels, full of incense;

**63** one young bull, one ram, one male lamb in its first year, for a burnt offering;

