**65** and for the sacrifice of peace offerings: two oxen, five rams, five male goats, five male lambs in their first year. This was the offering of Abidan the son of Gideoni.

---

**66** On the tenth day, the leader of the sons of Dan: Ahiezer the son of Ammishaddai.

**67** His offering was one silver dish, its weight one hundred and thirty shekels; one silver basin of seventy shekels, according to the shekel of the sanctuary, both of them full of fine flour mixed with oil for a grain offering;

**68** one golden dish of ten shekels, full of incense;

**69** one young bull, one ram, one male lamb in its first year, for a burnt offering;

